PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778569553
OL,3,CTaiwan's opposition leader defends
OL,4,Ccloser ties with China ahead of Trump
OL,5,Ctrip
OL,7,FTaiwan's opposition leader Cheng Li-
OL,8,Fwun, who met Xi Jinping in April,
OL,9,Fspoke to ITV News Asia Correspondent
OL,10,FDebi Edward
OL,12,FThe first thing that strikes you when
OL,13,Fyou meet Cheng Li-wun is her height,
OL,14,Fthen her energy, which matches her six-
OL,15,Ffoot stature.
OL,17,FThe Chairwoman of the Kuomintang
OL,18,F(KMT), the opposition party in Taiwan,
OL,19,Fis riding high on the notoriety she
OL,20,Fhas gained from her meeting last month
OL,21,Fwith Chinese President Xi Jinping.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778569553
OL,3,CTaiwan's opposition leader defends
OL,4,Ccloser ties with China ahead of Trump
OL,5,Ctrip
OL,7,FA lot has changed in the decade since
OL,8,Fthe KMT last met with the Communist
OL,9,Fleader in 2016, and in the words of
OL,10,Fthe chairwoman, the island "is now at
OL,11,Fa critical crossroads, a pivotal
OL,12,Fmoment that will determine whether
OL,13,Fcross-strait relations veer towards
OL,14,Fpeace or war".
OL,16,FShe came into her leadership role in
OL,17,FNovember last year and has prioritised
OL,18,Fa meeting with Xi and re-engaging in
OL,19,Fdialogue with the Chinese Communist
OL,20,FParty (CCP).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778569553
OL,3,CTaiwan's opposition leader defends
OL,4,Ccloser ties with China ahead of Trump
OL,5,Ctrip
OL,7,FWe met her on the day the deadlock
OL,8,Fover Taiwan's defence budget was
OL,9,Fbroken. The ruling Democratic
OL,10,FProgressive Party (DPP) had put
OL,11,Fforward an increased budget, but that
OL,12,Fwas opposed by the KMT, which has a
OL,13,Fmajority of seats in the parliament.
OL,15,FFinally, after months of wrangling and
OL,16,Fstalemate, a smaller increase was
OL,17,Fapproved, most of which will go
OL,18,Ftowards buying US arms such as defence
OL,19,Fsystems and missiles.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778569553
OL,3,CTaiwan's opposition leader defends
OL,4,Ccloser ties with China ahead of Trump
OL,5,Ctrip
OL,7,FCheng Li-wun had wanted defence
OL,8,Fspending to be even lower, believing
OL,9,Fthat the DPP's focus on a military
OL,10,Fbuild-up of Taiwan is provoking the
OL,11,Fmainland.
OL,13,FShe said if the KMT returns to power
OL,14,Fin the 2028 elections, her party,
OL,15,Fperhaps with her as President, will
OL,16,Fpromise peaceful cross-strait
OL,17,Frelations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778569553
OL,3,CTaiwan's opposition leader defends
OL,4,Ccloser ties with China ahead of Trump
OL,5,Ctrip
OL,7,FDuring her meeting with President Xi,
OL,8,Fhe told her that reunification is an
OL,9,Finevitability, and she has said she
OL,10,Fwould continue discussions with the
OL,11,FCommunist Party if the KMT is the
OL,12,Fruling party.
OL,14,FOur interview was conducted mostly in
OL,15,FChinese, but she switched to English
OL,16,Fwhen I challenged her on whether, in
OL,17,Fany peaceful deal with China, that
OL,18,Fwould mean giving up Taiwanese
OL,19,Fdemocracy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778569553
OL,3,CTaiwan's opposition leader defends
OL,4,Ccloser ties with China ahead of Trump
OL,5,Ctrip
OL,7,FI told her I found it hard to believe
OL,8,Fthat the Communist Party would
OL,9,Fcontinue to allow a part of China to
OL,10,Fbe a voting democracy.
OL,12,FCheng insisted it is something she can
OL,13,Fachieve.
OL,15,F"Yes, yes, yes," she said, moving
OL,16,Fforward in her seat, and sending the
OL,17,Fmicrophones peaking.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778569553
OL,3,CTaiwan's opposition leader defends
OL,4,Ccloser ties with China ahead of Trump
OL,5,Ctrip
OL,7,FShe claimed it was something she would
OL,8,F"prove to the world" and that she had
OL,9,Fbelieved President Xi to be sincere
OL,10,Fwhen he spoke of "respecting their
OL,11,Fdifferences."
OL,13,FShe rejected the similarities to Hong
OL,14,FKong and claimed any unification that
OL,15,Fdid not respect Taiwan's social
OL,16,Fsystem, its democracy and rule of law
OL,17,Fwould be fake.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778569553
OL,3,CTaiwan's opposition leader defends
OL,4,Ccloser ties with China ahead of Trump
OL,5,Ctrip
OL,7,FPresident Xi has talked of peaceful
OL,8,Freunification but hasn't ruled out
OL,9,Fmilitary action. The Taiwanese Air
OL,10,FForce is routinely scrambled to repel
OL,11,FChinese incursions, and every few
OL,12,Fmonths, Beijing conducts large-scale
OL,13,Fexercises around Taiwan's shores.
OL,15,FWe also met with Taiwan's Deputy
OL,16,FForeign Minister ahead of the Trump-Xi
OL,17,Fsummit, and he told me Taiwan won't be
OL,18,Fthreatened into reunification, and
OL,19,Fthat it was a mistake of Cheng Li-wun
OL,20,Fnot to have conveyed that message
OL,21,Fclearly to Xi Jinping.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778569553
OL,3,CTaiwan's opposition leader defends
OL,4,Ccloser ties with China ahead of Trump
OL,5,Ctrip
OL,7,FChen Ming-chi said the KMT did not
OL,8,Fspeak for the majority of Taiwanese
OL,9,Fpeople and accused her of only echoing
OL,10,Fthe view of China.
OL,12,FOne of Taiwan's greatest defences
OL,13,Fcould be its importance to the global
OL,14,Feconomy. It is the world's biggest
OL,15,Fproducer of semiconductors, the chips
OL,16,Fused in everything from phones to
OL,17,Ffighter jets.
OL,19,FI asked Chen whether Taiwan could use
OL,20,Fits economic might to deter China, and
OL,21,Findeed America, from conflict.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778569553
OL,3,CTaiwan's opposition leader defends
OL,4,Ccloser ties with China ahead of Trump
OL,5,Ctrip
OL,7,FHe said Taiwan would not weaponise its
OL,8,Fimportant status in the global supply
OL,9,Fchain, where it is a ''good and
OL,10,Ftrusted partner of the world".
OL,12,FHe said that the message had been
OL,13,Fconveyed to Donald Trump, and they
OL,14,Fbelieve he understood it very well.
OL,26,@rD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778569553
OL,3,CTaiwan's opposition leader defends
OL,4,Ccloser ties with China ahead of Trump
OL,5,Ctrip
OL,7,FHe did not give me a direct yes or no
OL,8,Fanswer when I questioned whether he
OL,9,Ftrusted Trump to protect Taiwan during
OL,10,Fhis time in office; instead, the
OL,11,Fdeputy foreign minister said he
OL,12,Fbelieved in the US and repeated that
OL,13,F''it was in America's interest, in the
OL,14,Finterests of the whole world, to
OL,15,Fmaintain the status quo".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
