PN,31412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778569553
OL,3,CTaiwan's opposition leader defends
OL,4,Ccloser ties with China ahead of Trump
OL,5,Ctrip
OL,7,FThere will be no Taiwanese politicians
OL,8,Fat the table when President Xi meets
OL,9,FPresident Trump in Beijing. It can
OL,10,Fsometimes feel like the future of
OL,11,FTaiwan is not in the hands of those
OL,12,Fwho matter most.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
